{"tid":1579550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下大家9.21冷靜一晚！","createTime":"2019-09-18T15:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T02:51:10.000Z","uid":38503,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"bbef88e71d627517a79b0a809506484f9bc08727","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"冇幾十張百張A4紙事少<br />\n出起事上嚟就真係送頭<br />\n各位手足忍一晚半晚<br />\n9.21堆藍絲廢老同黑社會明顯有人保先咁張揚<br />\n唔係話淆唔淆驚唔驚 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係冇必要出手！</span></strong></span><br />\n我哋守護嘅唔係A4紙同墨水 有大撚把！<br />\n留返啖氣係10.1一次爆曬出嚟<br />\n文宣嘅嘢交返俾我哋<br />\n我哋已經準備好晒新海報牆紙粉 包保實到佢哋指甲反撚埋都撕唔走<br />\n就由班垃圾幫我地清清佢 去舊迎新<br />\n<br />\n佢哋撕一我哋貼萬 <br />\n下世會齊齊做樹去還債<br />\n<br />\n前線嘅手足請好好休息一天<br />\n連儂牆一日半日就可以還原<br />\n唔好因為一隻何妖就送頭<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫推<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"42946a8a18915f74fedf916a4508267e754c0564","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0108d9603927966a4f20539f468f2cf6c9c01769","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d40743e0dc14f26afd29b8fff011ccbacc04fe78","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e64cbeb53754a84e8183320ceb3ad61ae12fb132","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:12.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"0e7ae7fd92c48354ff3424b463b46c55a8c81f5e","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:24.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"24e7d92cc6ebe05c0a92280359fee6d9af1d118a","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"66570c437534ba734aad93aababbbcce3e82968e","tid":1579550,"uid":38503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi